---
// Component Imports
import MainHead from '../components/MainHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer/index.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header/index.astro';
---
<html lang="en" class="overflow-x-hidden">
  <head>
    <MainHead title="Frank Stallone Portfolio" desc="The portfolio, blog and chronicles of misadventures for Frank Stallone III" />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden relative mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <Header />
    <figure class="grid gap-8 p-4 place-items-center md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 lg:grid-rows-3 overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/assets/me.jpg" class="xs:square lg:row-span-2 lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1" alt="Photograph of me, Frank Stallone III">
      <figcaption class="h-full flex place-items-center md:col-span-3 lg:col-span-4 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-2">
        <h2 class="text-amber-amber12 md:leading-snug py-8 text-4xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-8xl">üëãüèº Hiya! I love <span class="font-black text-red-red11 tracking-tight">TECHNOLOGY</span>, <span class="font-black text-red-red11 tracking-tight">MINDFULNESS</span>, <span class="italic mr-2 xl:mr-4">and</span> <span class="font-black text-red-red11 tracking-tight">CREATING</span> compelling user experiences.</h2>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <main class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="sr-only">Featured work</h2>
      <div class="xs:my-8">
        <h3 class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-amber12">Roll by ADP</h3>
        <h4 class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-semibold text-amber-amber11">UX, UI, Design System</h4>
        <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-semibold">Fluent in translating scribbles and seemingly nonsensical gibberish from a whiteboard into a full featured, high fidelity component for engineering integration. </p>
        <article class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 md:grid-rows-2 lg:grid-cols-8 lg:grid-rows-8 pb-4">
          <a href="#" class="xs:square md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 lg:col-span-4 lg:row-span-4 lg:row-start-2"><img src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-01@2x.png" alt="Mock up of the original logo design for Roll by ADP"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square lg:row-start-2 lg:col-start-7 lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2"><img src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-02@2x.png" alt="Screenshot of VSCode showing the design tokens repository for Roll by ADP"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square lg:row-start-5 lg:col-start-6 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-3"><img src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-03@2x.png" alt="Screenshot of the payroll run conversation UI showcasing the components design and created for our clients"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square lg:row-start-1 lg:col-start-5 lg:row-span-2 lg:col-span-2"><img src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-04@2x.png" alt="Screenshots of the mobile app that would eventually be used circa 2018"></a>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-50 h-full w-full lg:col-start-3"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden md:block bg-roll-100 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-4"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-200 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-3"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-300 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-4"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-400 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-5"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-500 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-600 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-4 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-700 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-800 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-roll-900 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-6"></div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="xs:my-8">
        <h3 class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-amber12">Builders Trust Capital</h3>
        <h4 class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-semibold text-amber-amber11 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3">Logo, Branding, UX, UI, Styleguide, WordPress Theme &amp; Hosting</h4>
        <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-semibold">Created a sophisticated brand that appealed to their entrepreneur clientele and resonated with their core values of trust, stability and transparency. </p>
        <article class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 md:grid-rows-2 lg:grid-cols-8 lg:grid-rows-8 pb-4">
          <a href="#" class="xs:square md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 lg:col-span-4 lg:row-span-4 lg:row-start-2"><img src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-01@2x.png" alt="Photo of initial sketches of the chosen logo for Builders Trust Capital showing the intentions for the three pilars"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square lg:row-start-2 lg:col-start-7 lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2"><img src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-02@2x.png" alt="Screenshot of the home page design for Builders Trust Capital"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square lg:row-start-5 lg:col-start-6 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-3"><img src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-03@2x.png" alt="Screenshot of the presentation for the new Builders Trust Capital logo in context on a sign and business cards"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square lg:row-start-1 lg:col-start-5 lg:row-span-2 lg:col-span-2"><img src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-04@2x.png" alt="Logo presentation of the Builders Trust Capital mark and logo type"></a>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-50 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-3"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-100 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-4"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-200 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-3"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden md:block bg-gold-300 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-4"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-400 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-5"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-500 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-5 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-600 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-4 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-700 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-800 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-6"></div>
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="square hidden lg:block bg-gold-900 rounded-lg h-full w-full lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-6"></div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="xs:my-8">
        <h3 class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-amber12">NJC Stone Supply</h3>
        <h4 class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-semibold text-amber-amber11">Logo</h4>
        <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-semibold">Designed a logo mark and logo type that speaks equally to Noah's audience as it does Noah's work.</p>
        <article class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 pb-4">
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-01@2x.png" alt="The logo mark for Noah James Curtis Stone Supply &amp; Tree Service"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-02@2x.png" alt="The typeface and colors chosen for the branding of Noah James Curtis Stone Supply &amp; Tree Service"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-03@2x.png" alt="Screenshot of the grid used for one of the Noah James Curtis Stone Supply logos with type"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-04@2x.png" alt="One of the variations of the NJC Stone Supply &amp; Tree Service with logo mark and type logo"></a>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="xs:my-8">
        <h3 class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-amber12">Brackets Podcast</h3>
        <h4 class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-semibold text-amber-amber11">Co-host, Logo, Branding</h4>
        <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-semibold">Co-create a technology podcast that serves as the pulse of tech within ADP.</p>
        <article class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 pb-4">
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-01@2x.png" alt="The original logo mark and type logo for ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-02@2x.png" alt="The original logo mark for ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-03@2x.png" alt="Play on the ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast logo"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-04@2x.png" alt="Another spin of the design of the ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast logo"></a>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="xs:my-8">
        <h3 class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-amber12">Savani</h3>
        <h4 class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-semibold text-amber-amber11">Logo, Branding</h4>
        <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-semibold">Brought a niche Volkswagen parts company closer to it's audience with new branding.</p>
        <article class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 pb-4">
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-01@2x.png" alt="The original logo mark for Savani Auto Parts"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-02@2x.png" alt="The type logo for Savani Auto Parts"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-03@2x.png" alt="The logo mark and type logo for Savani Auto Parts"></a>
          <a href="#" class="xs:square"><img src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-04@2x.png" alt="A t-shirt with the Savani Auto Parts logo mark and type logo"></a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
